creator: n-gage.io
descriptionHtml:
Get interactive and start your adventure with the Jimmy’s Farm & Wildlife Park app. Your guide companion for use before, during and after a visit!

Download and register before you arrive to receive special app-only offers, plan your day and explore the park. Use the app during your visit to learn more about your favourite animals and unlock hidden information. Even get live updates from our Rangers!

Test your knowledge with our fun quizzes. Use the interactive map to navigate the park with ease. Get reminders about Ranger talk schedules, special offers and then capture your day with our custom photo frames to save or share.

If you’re a member get access to your exclusive discounts at our partner attractions.

After a visit, relive your experience and stay connected with exciting news and updates about the park. Experience more with Jimmy’s Farm & Wildlife Park and start your adventure right here!
descriptionShort: Share the Good Life with Jimmy’s Farm & Wildlife Park

- You can now view zone information on the map including opening hours, accessibility and other useful information.
- You are now able to hide past events in “Your Plan”.
- You can now leave feedback on events you have attended.
- In-app alerts have been added, including success, errors and offline detection to improve the overall app user experience.
